<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        @page { margin: 22px 24px; }
        body { font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9px; color: #000; }
        .header { width: 100%; border-bottom: 1px solid #999; padding-bottom: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .header td { vertical-align: middle; }
        .header .logo { width: 66px; }
        .header .logo img { max-height: 56px; max-width: 60px; }
        .header .school { text-align: center; }
        .header .school .name { font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px; }
        .header .school .ministry { font-size: 9px; }
        .header .school .tel { font-size: 8px; }
        .title-row { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .title-row td { font-size: 11px; }
        .title-row .right { text-align: right; }
        .title-row b { font-weight: bold; }
        table.list { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        table.list th, table.list td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 3px 4px; font-size: 8.5px; }
        table.list th { text-align: center; font-weight: bold; background: #f2f2f2; }
        table.list td.center { text-align: center; }
        table.list .grp-g { background: #eaf2fb; }
        table.list .grp-f { background: #fbeef4; }
        table.list .grp-t { background: #eef7ee; }
        table.list tr.grand td { background: #dfe6ee; font-weight: bold; }
        .note { font-size: 8px; color: #666; margin-top: 5px; }
        .footer { width: 100%; margin-top: 14px; font-size: 9px; }
        .footer td { vertical-align: top; }
        .footer .sign { text-align: right; text-decoration: underline; }
        .footer .date .line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; display: inline-block; width: 130px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <table class="header">
        <tr>
            <td class="logo">{% if logo_data %}<img src="{{ logo_data }}" alt="Logo">{% endif %}</td>
            <td class="school">
                <div class="name">{{ school ? school.name|upper : '' }}</div>
                <div class="ministry">{{ school ? school.sousTutelle : '' }}</div>
                <div class="tel">Tel: {{ school ? school.phone : '' }}</div>
            </td>
            <td class="logo"></td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <table class="title-row">
        <tr>
            <td><b>ADMISSION, REDOUBLEMENT ET EXCLUSION — APPROCHE GENRE</b></td>
            <td class="right"><b>Année Scolaire:</b> {{ school_year ? school_year.name : '—' }}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <table class="list">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th rowspan="2" style="width:22%">Niveau</th>
                <th colspan="4" class="grp-g">Garçons</th>
                <th colspan="4" class="grp-f">Filles</th>
                <th colspan="4" class="grp-t">Total</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th class="grp-g">Noté</th><th class="grp-g">Adm.</th><th class="grp-g">Red.</th><th class="grp-g">Exc.</th>
                <th class="grp-f">Noté</th><th class="grp-f">Adm.</th><th class="grp-f">Red.</th><th class="grp-f">Exc.</th>
                <th class="grp-t">Noté</th><th class="grp-t">Adm.</th><th class="grp-t">Red.</th><th class="grp-t">Exc.</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {% for lvl in levels %}
                <tr>
                    <td>{{ lvl.label }}</td>
                    <td class="center">{{ lvl.g.noted }}</td><td class="center">{{ lvl.g.admis }}</td><td class="center">{{ lvl.g.redouble }}</td><td class="center">0</td>
                    <td class="center">{{ lvl.f.noted }}</td><td class="center">{{ lvl.f.admis }}</td><td class="center">{{ lvl.f.redouble }}</td><td class="center">0</td>
                    <td class="center">{{ lvl.graded }}</td><td class="center">{{ lvl.admis }}</td><td class="center">{{ lvl.redouble }}</td><td class="center">0</td>
                </tr>
            {% else %}
                <tr><td colspan="13" class="center">Aucune donnée disponible</td></tr>
            {% endfor %}
            {% if levels is not empty %}
                <tr class="grand">
                    <td>TOTAL</td>
                    <td class="center">{{ overall.g.noted }}</td><td class="center">{{ overall.g.admis }}</td><td class="center">{{ overall.g.redouble }}</td><td class="center">0</td>
                    <td class="center">{{ overall.f.noted }}</td><td class="center">{{ overall.f.admis }}</td><td class="center">{{ overall.f.redouble }}</td><td class="center">0</td>
                    <td class="center">{{ overall.graded }}</td><td class="center">{{ overall.admis }}</td><td class="center">{{ overall.redouble }}</td><td class="center">0</td>
                </tr>
            {% endif %}
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="note">
        Décision calculée sur la moyenne annuelle : Admis (Adm.) si moyenne &gt;= 10/20, sinon Redouble (Red.).
        L'exclusion (Exc.) n'étant pas déductible automatiquement des notes, elle est laissée à 0.
    </div>

    <table class="footer">
        <tr>
            <td class="date"><span class="line">&nbsp;</span> le {{ generated_at|date('d/m/Y H:i:s') }}</td>
            <td class="sign">Signature</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
